OL,3,CBBC board member quits citing
OL,4,C'governance issues' at corporation
OL,6,FA member of the BBC'S board has
OL,7,Fresigned, citing "governance issues"
OL,8,Fat the corporation.
OL,10,FShumeet Banerji announced he would be
OL,11,Fleaving on Friday, less than two weeks
OL,12,Fafter Tim Davie resigned from his role
OL,13,Fas the BBC's director general along
OL,14,Fwith Deborah Turness as BBC News chief
OL,15,Fexecutive.
OL,17,FA BBC spokesman confirmed the news,
OL,18,Fsaying: "Shumeet Banerji today
OL,19,Fnotified the BBC Board of his
OL,20,Fresignation.
