OL,6,F"Mr Banerji's term on the board as a
OL,7,Fnon-executive director was due to end
OL,8,Fat the end of December and we thank
OL,9,Fhim for his service.
OL,11,F"The search for a replacement is
OL,12,Falready well under way and we will
OL,13,Fupdate further in due course."
OL,15,FBanerji had said in a letter that he
OL,16,Fwas "not consulted" about the events
OL,17,Fwhich led up to the resignations of
OL,18,FDavie and Turness, BBC News reported.
