OL,3,CBBC board member quits citing
OL,4,C'governance issues' at corporation
OL,6,FAs one of the non-executive directors
OL,7,Fon the BBC board, Banerji was
OL,8,Fresponsible for upholding and
OL,9,Fprotecting the independence of the
OL,10,Fcorporation by acting in the public
OL,11,Finterest and exercising independent
OL,12,Fjudgment, according to a profile on
OL,13,Fits website.
OL,15,FHe was also responsible for ensuring
OL,16,Fthe board's decision-making was in the
OL,17,Fpublic interest.
OL,19,FHe had been in the role since January
OL,20,F2022.
